TestNG -- Test Next Generation. It is framework.


It is an Open source framework.
It is only Java based framework.

Advantages:
1. Purpose -- Design test cases in a systematic ways
2. Generated html reports
3. Lot of annotations
4. We can define sequence of test cases using priorities
5. Dependency feature it means one test case depend on other test cases.
6. Grouping
7. Data Provider -- Suppose if we want to execute login features with multiple set of data then data provider helpfull


TestNG is called as TDD Framework. Test driven development framework.

